description: AMUNDI NASDAQ-100 UCITS ETF - DAILY HEDGED EUR (C) seeks to replicate as closely as possible the performance of the NASDAQ-100 Index in Euros, whether the trend is rising or falling and has a monthly currency hedging in EUR. This ETF enables investors to benefit from an exposure, with a single transaction, to the 100 Non-Financial listed on the NASDAQ stocks including technological, Internet and IT sectors. For further information, please also refer to the fund prospectus.
name: Amundi NASDAQ-100 UCITS ETF - Daily Hedged EUR
